Class SEQLifter

  • java.lang.Object
    • ir.compiler.SEQLifter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Visitor<java.util.List<IRStm>>

    public class SEQLifter
extends java.lang.Object
implements Visitor<java.util.List<IRStm>>
    IR SEQ lifters. A SEQ lifter is used to flatten an IR program into a sequential list of statements, removing all SEQ and ESEQ nodes in the process.
